{"3874620": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Party Me", "steam_appid": 3874620, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Me</strong> 是一款以隊伍為基礎的冒險遊戲，結合文字玩法與 roguelite 元素，在遊戲中你需要面對永久失去同伴的風險。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個由獸人等怪物居住的村莊裡，你需要將它們招募進隊伍，並踏上冒險之旅以變得更強。面對籠罩在村莊之上的威脅，透過擊敗魔王或騎士團來帶來和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/81067f02b7a221dd5675d524ea190960.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/20cb1e78153f50e5f26492d05f5ecc9a.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >殘酷的怪物威脅著村莊並屠殺人類，正席捲整個世界。然而，希望仍然存在。儘管這些怪物——被肉慾驅使——進行無情的屠殺與暴力行為，卻會拋棄自己的後代。這些在村莊中被撫養長大的怪物之子，最終將成長為能夠代替脆弱人類對抗魔王的終極戰士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隊伍制遊戲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/cad9ebf740be430e92d2ed1f9061adb3.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/67b02971f5417a52d928b9978a2e0e11.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與適合不同探索的同伴互動以獲取物品，並與旅途中遇到的怪物戰鬥來獲得戰利品。將這些戰利品組合起來以製作更有用的裝備，或在市場上出售。隨著同伴累積經驗並變得更強，抵禦逐漸逼近的威脅，守護村莊的和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>運氣</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/741094893f4b6f64ad927ef727ef7c2e.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/7755df72ad63235d7deae054ccd7f733.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然遊戲的很大一部分由運氣決定，但核心挑戰在於管理機率以達成理想結果。即使失去了寶貴的同伴或物品，只要堅持朝著目標前進，依然可以完成遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/7338c74839d2e7f0c86bcb2668a85a8a.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party Me</strong> 是一款以隊伍為基礎的冒險遊戲，結合文字玩法與 roguelite 元素，在遊戲中你需要面對永久失去同伴的風險。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一個由獸人等怪物居住的村莊裡，你需要將它們招募進隊伍，並踏上冒險之旅以變得更強。面對籠罩在村莊之上的威脅，透過擊敗魔王或騎士團來帶來和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/81067f02b7a221dd5675d524ea190960.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/20cb1e78153f50e5f26492d05f5ecc9a.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >殘酷的怪物威脅著村莊並屠殺人類，正席捲整個世界。然而，希望仍然存在。儘管這些怪物——被肉慾驅使——進行無情的屠殺與暴力行為，卻會拋棄自己的後代。這些在村莊中被撫養長大的怪物之子，最終將成長為能夠代替脆弱人類對抗魔王的終極戰士。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隊伍制遊戲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/cad9ebf740be430e92d2ed1f9061adb3.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/67b02971f5417a52d928b9978a2e0e11.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與適合不同探索的同伴互動以獲取物品，並與旅途中遇到的怪物戰鬥來獲得戰利品。將這些戰利品組合起來以製作更有用的裝備，或在市場上出售。隨著同伴累積經驗並變得更強，抵禦逐漸逼近的威脅，守護村莊的和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>運氣</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/741094893f4b6f64ad927ef727ef7c2e.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/7755df72ad63235d7deae054ccd7f733.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然遊戲的很大一部分由運氣決定，但核心挑戰在於管理機率以達成理想結果。即使失去了寶貴的同伴或物品，只要堅持朝著目標前進，依然可以完成遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/extras/7338c74839d2e7f0c86bcb2668a85a8a.avif?t=1775737959\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>", "short_description": "《Party Me》是一款以團隊為主題的 RPG 遊戲。訓練怪物後代，在致命的困境中求生，重建失落的世界——這是一款基於運氣、永久死亡的養成類 RPG 遊戲。", "supported_languages": "英文, 韓文, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 保加利亞文, 捷克文, 丹麥文, 荷蘭文, 芬蘭文, 希臘文, 匈牙利文, 印尼語, 日文, 挪威文, 波蘭文, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 羅馬尼亞文, 俄文, 簡體中文, 瑞典文, 泰文, 繁體中文, 土耳其文, 烏克蘭文, 越南文, 印地語", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/fecef1ad4d025d2613243dd03746774933b28516/header.jpg?t=1775737959", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/955dd40051e96b80cc167d196c819ad68795e57d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1775737959", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3874620/955dd40051e96b80cc167d196c819ad68795e57d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1775737959", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7, 8, 8.1, 10 x64<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Pentium E2180 or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 1 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> GeForce 7600 GT (256 MB)<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7, 8, 8.1, 10 x64<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3-3240 or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 2 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> GeForce 8800 GTS (512 MB)<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 2 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026 第 2 季"}}}}